                            3. tentukan luas permukaan dan volume bangun bola berikut!​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>Luas Permukaan : 1.808,64</p><p>Volume : 7.234,56</p><p></p><p><strong>Penjelasan dengan langkah-langkah:</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>L</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>n</strong><strong>g</strong><strong>k</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>h</strong><strong> </strong><strong>-</strong><strong> </strong><strong>l</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>n</strong><strong>g</strong><strong>k</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>h</strong><strong> </strong><strong>a</strong><strong>d</strong><strong>a</strong><strong> </strong><strong>d</strong><strong>i</strong><strong> </strong><strong>d</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>l</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>m</strong><strong> </strong><strong>g</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>m</strong><strong>b</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>r</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong><strong>_</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>M</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>p</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>l</strong><strong> </strong><strong>:</strong><strong> </strong><strong>M</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>t</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>m</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>t</strong><strong>i</strong><strong>k</strong><strong>a</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>※</strong><strong> </strong><strong>J</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>d</strong><strong>i</strong><strong>k</strong><strong>a</strong><strong