                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="d-10cm-tentukan-luas-permukaan-dan-volume-bangun-bola-berikut">
                            5. d= 10cm tentukan luas permukaan dan volume bangun bola berikut</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>maafkan saya kalau salah</p><p></p><p><strong>Penjelasan dengan langkah-langkah:</strong></p><p>Luas permukaan = 4πr²</p><p>= 4π5.5</p><p>=100π cm²</p><p></p><p>Volume = 4/3πr³</p><p>= 4/3 π 5.5.5 </p><p>=166,6π cm³</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tentukan-luas-permukaan-dan-volume-bangun-bola-berikut%e2%80%8b">
                            6. tentukan luas permukaan dan volume bangun bola berikut​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Diketahui</strong><strong>:</strong><strong> </strong></p><p><strong>diameter</strong><strong> </strong><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>1</strong><strong>2</strong><strong> </strong><strong>DM</strong></p><p><strong>jari </strong><strong>jari </strong><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>1</strong><strong>/</strong><strong>2</strong><strong> </strong><strong>dari </strong><strong>1</strong><strong>2</strong><strong> </strong><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>6</strong><strong> </strong><strong>dm</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Ditanyakan</strong><strong>:</strong><strong> </strong><strong>luas</strong><strong> </strong><strong>permukaan</strong><strong> </strong><strong>dan</strong><strong> </strong><strong>volume</strong><strong> </strong><strong>bangun</strong><strong> </strong><strong>bola</strong><strong> </strong><strong>tsb</strong><strong>?</strong><strong> </strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Jawab</strong><strong>:</strong><strong> </strong></p><p></p><p><strong>luas</strong><strong> </strong><strong>permukaan</strong><strong>:</strong><strong> </strong></p><p><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>4</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x</strong><strong> </strong><strong>π</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x</strong><strong> </strong><strong>r²</strong></p><p><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>4</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x</strong><strong> </strong><strong>3</strong><strong>,</strong><strong>1</strong><strong>4</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x </strong><strong>6</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x </strong><strong>6</strong></p><p><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>4</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x</strong><strong> </strong><strong>3</strong><strong>,</strong><strong>1</strong><strong>4</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x</strong><strong> </strong><strong>3</strong><strong>6</strong></p><p><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>4</strong><strong>5</strong><strong>2</strong><strong>,</strong><strong>1</strong><strong>6</strong><strong> </strong><strong>dm</strong><strong> </strong></p><p></p><p></p><p><strong>volume</strong><strong> </strong><strong>bola:</strong></p><p><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>4</strong><strong>/</strong><strong>3</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x</strong><strong> </strong><strong>π</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x</strong><strong> </strong><strong>r³</strong></p><p><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>4</strong><strong>/</strong><strong>3</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x </strong><strong>3</strong><strong>,</strong><strong>1</strong><strong>4</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x </strong><strong>6</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x </strong><strong>6</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x </strong><strong>6</strong></p><p><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>4</strong><strong>/</strong><strong>3</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x </strong><strong>3</strong><strong>,</strong><strong>1</strong><strong>4</strong><strong> </strong><strong>x </strong><strong>2</strong><strong>1</strong><strong>6</strong></p><p><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>9</strong><strong>0</strong><strong>4</strong><strong>,</strong><strong>3</strong><strong>2</strong><strong> </strong><strong>dm</strong></p><p></p><p></p><p><strong>semoga </strong><strong>bermanfaat </strong></p><p><strong>maaf </strong><strong>kalo </strong><strong>salah</strong></p><p>Luas Permukaan Bola</p><p>= 4πr²</p><p>= 4 × 3,14 × 6²</p><p>= 4 × 3,14 × 36</p><p>= 4 × 113,04</p><p>= 452,16 dm²</p><p></p><p>Volume Bola</p><p>= 4/3 × π × r³</p><p>= 4/3 × 3,14 × 6³</p><p>= 4/3 × 3,14 × 216</p><p>= 4 × 3,14 × 72</p><p>= 4 × 226,08</p><p>= 904,32 dm³</p><p></p><p>~Opung~</p><br />
